Package db

Class Cache

java.lang.Object
db.Cache
public class Cache extends Object
In memory cache. Allows effectively store, find, update records of the following format: 
 {
     "account": "234678", //long
     "name": "Иванов Иван Иванович", //string
     "value": "2035.34" //double
 }
All operations on cache have log(n) time cost, except size(), which has constant time complexity.
